    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156950/extras/ab5201e5516c61504cc189d7f1e0e358.poster.avif?t=1762833943\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156950/extras/ab5201e5516c61504cc189d7f1e0e358.webm?t=1762833943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156950/extras/ab5201e5516c61504cc189d7f1e0e358.mp4?t=1762833943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>当12岁的泰迪意外跌倒陷入昏迷时，他将一头扎进自己的潜意识：一个广阔的、拥有无限可能性的超现实世界。</strong><br><br>在一个名为“Proxy”的人工智能植入物的帮助下，泰迪必须去挖掘深深埋藏在他的思想中的、那令人敬畏的力量，并使用它从潜意识中逃脱；否则他将会永远被困在思想中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156950/extras/83a467171ac04bf7bd0e15d71296fc7d.poster.avif?t=1762833943\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156950/extras/83a467171ac04bf7bd0e15d71296fc7d.webm?t=1762833943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156950/extras/83a467171ac04bf7bd0e15d71296fc7d.mp4?t=1762833943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >超现实的冒险</h2>踏上一段无法预知的旅程，你将在令人费解的梦境中施展惊人的能力。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >轻松的探险体验</h2>跳跃，定点传送，滑行，滑翔在泰迪脑海中的每一个角落，并体验雪橇滑行带来的超高速刺激。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >出色的故事讲述</h2>华丽的视觉效果，动态相机和原创音乐的加持下，让你完全沉浸其中并有能力掌控属于你和泰迪的故事。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多重的情感连接</h2>Proxy不仅仅是你的同伴，向导和伙伴；他也将会是重新连接你破碎家庭的关键。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156950/extras/0eb30647857cd5580febda8ed71f7445.poster.avif?t=1762833943\" width=720 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156950/extras/0eb30647857cd5580febda8ed71f7445.webm?t=1762833943\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2156950/extras/0eb30647857cd5580febda8ed71f7445.mp4?t=1762833943\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
